details: Subject is a 57-year old citizen of El Salvador, an at-large illegal alien, currently wanted in El Salvador for homicide. It is alleged that in 2012, Chicas along with two other accomplices killed a young man. He is currently the subject of an Interpol Red Notice for the same offense. Chicas unlawfully entered the U.S. in 2014 and despite numerous attempts by ICE to locate his whereabouts, he currently remains at-large.
